00:36:17,420 --> 00:36:21,900
Interleukin 1, 6, Dicamoykin, Interleukin 17, Interferon Gamma.

625
00:36:22,600 --> 00:36:23,460
Plusieurs sources.

626
00:36:23,600 --> 00:36:27,460
Macrophages, cellules mastocytaires, lymphocytes T, cellules dendritiques,

627
00:36:27,560 --> 00:36:28,280
